{"type": "article", "id": 14175, "title": "微博炉专用餐具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-31T06:58:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151411bKEpjvnSMi9BGOtI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 认为，微波炉除了加热以外，其实还有很多功能被人无视了，而一项重要的原因是加热用具的缺失，于是最近他们推出了一系列微波炉专用器具，但是其目的却是希望能够提供用餐的全套需求，而不仅仅是加热食物。这套产品全部采用注射成型聚丙烯材料，使得微波炉使用安全健康，它包括为米饭，谷物，意面，加蛋准备的不同的容器，这些东西通常不是微波炉制作，但是有了合适的容器，他们也可以为用餐带来一些惊喜。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141747iSBugEP9qazXKtRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141747W7q2nZxUMtXwjvKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141748treP51hJqRHxLV24.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141748R27qMAVLGco1PNz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141749oIeQFhgiTnKvdXsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73290598\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141749MHvsrZl6OBj5KE1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85683761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141749Y1VNJyonA5D8g4cS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141750YhNkGu9tqOzdopCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141751CNTOfQykrg5SInmA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141751MQEXLZcYnBjFWRlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64316239\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141751JTki3vAnYK9jd2Nt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141752OHdA21nbhCsu58TU.jpg\" alt=\"\" dat